## 6. Types (`lib/types.ts`)

`Invoice` is a **single-line** model: one `description`, one `amount_before_tax`, tax fields, no `line_items` on the type.

Related: `Client`, `Profile`, `Payment`, `BankTransaction`, `Purchase`, `Organization`, `OrgMember`.

