## 7. Image upload / OCR

| Capability | Present? |
|------------|----------|
| Image upload (PNG/JPG) | **No** |
| OCR (Tesseract, Vision API, etc.) | **No** |
| Bank PDF | **Text extraction** (`pdf-parse`) + regex in `pdf-bank.ts` |
| File uploads | CSV/XLS/XLSX/PDF (bank), CSV (invoices) via `FormData` in `bank-statement-upload.tsx` and `invoice-import-modal.tsx` |

